After launch, I identified the opportunity to improve both visibility and efficiency. I proposed using ads to increase engagement and curiosity around the product, which helped strengthen awareness. At the same time, I noticed that the manual order-processing system would slow the team down as demand grew, so I redesigned the workflow by upgrading the website and building an **n8n automation flow**. This significantly reduced manual work, making the order journey nearly automated from submission to processing, with the team mainly focused on shipping.
